The paper discusses the feasibility of using Attribute-Based Encryption (ABE) for secure management of Internet-of-Things (IoT) devices, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR) and IoT (cs.IOT). The paper also discusses the implementation of ABE on specific IoT platforms, which could fall under the categories of cyber-physical systems (cs.CYBER), software engineering (cs.SE), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
